       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. UNSTRING-BASIC.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-INPUT PIC X(20) VALUE "John Doe".
       01 WS-FIRST PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
       01 WS-LAST  PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           UNSTRING WS-INPUT DELIMITED BY SPACE
               INTO WS-FIRST WS-LAST
           END-UNSTRING
           DISPLAY "First: [" WS-FIRST "]"
           DISPLAY "Last:  [" WS-LAST "]"
           STOP RUN.
